      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok thanks. actually now that i'm looking in the mirror the redness is spreading a bit and the discharge is kind of thick and yellowish/greenish. i'm a bit worried it might be more than just dry eyes but i really don't have time to go to a clinic right now. do u think i could just try using some leftover antibiotic drops i have from an old infection a few months ago? would that be faster than waiting for an appointment?",
